{"tid":538004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊人撬門潛日式餐廳　抬走無錢夾萬","createTime":"2018-01-23T08:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T08:30:21.000Z","uid":66246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6de4d12e542b7da011304134d4da42a2eeb54925","tid":538004,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"創興廣場一間日式餐廳遭賊人撬門潛入，抬走店內一個無錢夾萬。下午2時許，彌敦道601號創興廣場五樓一間日式餐廳職員報警指，店門遭人撬開，店內一個夾萬被抬走，惟夾萬內無任何現金。據了解，賊人由後門潛入，抬走無錢夾萬。警員接報上門調查，惟負責人否認被爆竊，稱警察只是上門查酒牌。"},{"pid":"593c6de3bcba252d21c1c0e9c6ad28297e9db38e","tid":538004,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e68197d21e48fccd41b0f3347cf0e89b62e0fc1","tid":538004,"uid":90766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed31cff56aa01c53d12d0d73dd2ab316f761b6f","tid":538004,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/162439_cb663e47479c1ef875ee0e292c9b539b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F162439_cb663e47479c1ef875ee0e292c9b539b.png&h=18a854ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ddd5f2be3b63a0f63558f692685711a73f24003","tid":538004,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"警員接報上門調查，<span style=\"color: red;\">惟負責人否認被爆竊</span>，稱警察只是上門查酒牌。<br />\n<br />\n呃保險,黑錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4524b2d28783ce6e62e495869051e764ae2be6","tid":538004,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"班賊今晚會唔會放火燒鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189a7d35fd401391dd23bb1